title: ILO change for Sake holders
body:
SakeSwap should change the function on how Sake holders can participate in any new ILO project.

It should be made MANDATORY that if you want to participate/invest in any new ILO on Sakeswap, that the investment be bought with Sake tokens instead of ETH.  This will create a higher demand for Sake, and therefore pumping the price of Sake to the moon.  

**ALL SAKE HOLDERS BENEFIT FROM THIS**

Vote YES if you agree!
Vote No if you disagree!

Please note if you disagree, this will just drive the Sake price down.
choices: Yes I agree- lets pump the price
